Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真行啊 那麼多天不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了又不去上學了 就會在床上滾來滾去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 我自己會收拾 你出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 啊 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波說今晚要開個誓師集會 你去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 總之先在車站前見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說鶴見同學是不是完全不知悔改啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得就好像只有你最懂松雪君一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高一百八十一公分 體重六十八千克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的食物是八橋煎餅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興趣是女裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女裝?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等下...鶴見同學 話還沒說完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不帶你這樣到處說的 再怎麼說我也...  -疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛來嘛 動起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是迎接明天面碼成佛的大宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要裝飾得像模像樣地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼要用紙巾做花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你一個主角還動什麼手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很好玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 做得不錯嘛 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 別在那發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用傳單做垃圾箱 垃圾箱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?哦...垃圾箱?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:04:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-以前啊 我在班上不是被稱為味增渣嗎  -哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:04:01.46,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(指派不上用場的人 被其他孩子排除在外)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能做些傻事吸引別人的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 仁太和大家總是帶我一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過結果我也只是看著大家而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看著而已...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 所以啊 這次就全都交給我來辦好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要盛大地送你成佛 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底要胡鬧到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群孩子 到底要...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?為什麼啊聰君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別激動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽啊 你知道我身高有多少公分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我長高了很多 這一年裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很寂寞吧 聰志是 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能忘得了芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不掉就忘不掉 只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們都一樣寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 我 聰志 三個人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火升空之後嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「要是沒有面碼就好了」我以前曾經想過很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為要是沒有面碼 和仁太最好的人就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有了面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和仁太的距離反而越來越遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在距離又縮短了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這也是因為面碼回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得慶倖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去秘密基地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和安城在一起?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?嗯 在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你還叫囂著要讓面碼成佛 一到關鍵時刻你又怕了  -不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠沒出息的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為害怕 就逃避面碼 和安城在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想找個同病相憐的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天面碼打電話叫我出來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她說「為了仁太有事想拜託」  -誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?雪集 鶴子說什麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是只有你才能辦到的事 anaru
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼他們還不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 反正明天能見到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.18,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們先開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買了些零食
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 不愧是鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~我愛你 雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,party啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅信著 我堅信你們會來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.52,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 這個我超喜歡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又聚在一起了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺終點更近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼和我們結成了超和平busters...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用講開場白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼主角面碼請向前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.62,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(謝謝各位今天為了面碼齊聚一堂)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.33,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(面碼明天就成佛了)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.85,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}(到最後都想和大家開開心心地 拜託大家了)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是面碼的發言!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 面碼 要吃這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好紅啊 我不愛吃辣的 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...辣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事呢 沒事的 吃一口吧 啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼餘興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣不只是吃吃喝喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是誓師大會嗎 好容易聚在一起了 搞點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餘興?要搞什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 比如...重現那天的那一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重現那一天在這裡發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡發生的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑!那有什麼好重現的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 仁太啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是喜歡面碼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊 面碼也在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-說啊...  -啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊 說啊 說啊 說啊 說啊 說啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說這...有必要這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊 說啊 說啊 說啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對面碼...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續這樣逃避 就和那天一樣了 仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼一言不發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是...撲簌撲簌地掉著眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也該哭得差不多了吧 丟死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是雪集教你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還不是明擺著的嗎 那天的回答...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等面碼成佛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不明不白稀裡糊塗地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠輸給早就已經不在的面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甘心這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子是不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己喜歡的人 永遠不會喜歡自己的那種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的 因為我喜歡雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集一直追著面碼的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切我全都看在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠誰能說得清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-等面碼成佛後 宿海就...  -怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 雪集絕對不會選擇我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算面碼成佛了 取代她的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城 會是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對!不對!什麼取代啊 雪集根本沒有這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了我再怎麼苦悶也不會和雪集交往的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡仁太啊 根本無以取代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 正因為無以取代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必須讓面碼成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊仁太 我居然做了那種煽風點火的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是覺得仿佛回到了那天 所有一切...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了那天...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 剛才那是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼也喜歡仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說 說是喜歡 可不只是朋友之間的那種喜歡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道哦 是想娶做新娘子那種喜歡對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼要是能像這樣正常長大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼是不是已經是仁太的新娘子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不正常也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不成佛 就這樣留在這裡不也好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成佛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎 可以轉世的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不成佛的話就轉不成嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想正常地和大家說話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:26.62,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可是 要是轉成菜青蟲了該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常地和大家說話...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太說喜歡你 你會怎麼回答他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說「為了仁太有事拜託」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡面碼...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很清楚...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成佛吧 好嗎 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我...還不行嗎 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 面碼 你知道轉世嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉世?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就算生命走到盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能變成小寶寶重生到這個世上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一定是人的寶寶 也許是貓寶寶 也許是花寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 絕對不會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是...只有一點...只有一點...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 再等一下 大家說要為我放花火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微...等一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那 先把傘之類的固定到花火上吧  -好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:37.96,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(參考資料http://www.ryusei.biz/festival/ryu04.html)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?鶴見?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可愛 鶴子像小時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉換心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-仁太 拿著這邊  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有股聞到過的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你叫聰君來的嗎 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要結束了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就這樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為面碼和我們利害相通...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會讓你成佛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 現在停止還來得及...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-宿海  -嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼一定會很高興的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要讓花火升空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還能停止 還能停止可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成佛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二!一二!一二!一二!一二...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 聰君力氣好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二!一二!一二!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就剩發射了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 做得相當好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我說 大家還有沒有什麼話忘了說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她弟弟也在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不喊名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!!我好開心!謝謝啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁太也說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多開始吧 再晚的話會吵到人家休息的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣了嗎?現在停止還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來得及...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火...升起來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇~天上開花啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在嗎?那 她還在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我居然在想...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「沒有消失 太好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀